- The "How It Works" page failed the web performance test. It is essential to investigate the cause of this failure and optimize the page to improve its load time.
insights: The pricing page has the lowest load time, at 232.39999999999418 milliseconds, indicating that it is well-optimized.
The blog page has a low load time, at 258 milliseconds, but a high Time to First Byte (TTFB), at 87.29999999998836 milliseconds, indicating that there is room for optimization.
The homepage load time is higher than the pricing and blog pages, indicating that there are elements on the page that need optimization.
